<h3 id="digest-based-keys">Digest-Based Keys</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Modeling a “normal” cache</li>
  <li>Using a digest as the key</li>
  <li>Running out of space?</li>
  <li>Least recently used</li>
</ul>

